Charles Quinlivan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Quinlivan 0 Charles Quinlivan (1924–1974) was a film and television actor in the United States in the 1950s, 1960s, and 1970s, best known as the star of the western movie Seven Guns to Mesa, and of the short-lived 1960 TV series Mr. Garlund.
